52:02.467 --> 52:05.667
- Hey, prag, Schillinger
sends his love.

52:06.200 --> 52:08.033
- Fuck off!

52:08.100 --> 52:09.133
- Hey!

52:09.200 --> 52:11.700
Break it up.

52:14.867 --> 52:16.567
[man wolf whistles]

52:20.767 --> 52:23.934
- Beecher, you wanted
to see me?

52:24.000 --> 52:26.400
- I need you to move me
to another cellblock.

52:26.467 --> 52:29.500
- All the cellblocks
are full.

52:29.567 --> 52:32.100
- Then move me to
another prison.

52:32.166 --> 52:35.033
- Do I look like a
travel agent to you?

52:37.100 --> 52:38.133
Beecher.

52:41.600 --> 52:42.967
- What?

52:47.667 --> 52:48.700
- Nothing.

53:23.233 --> 53:24.900
[grunting]

53:38.600 --> 53:40.533
[inmates yelling]

53:42.667 --> 53:44.533
- You're an animal!
You're an animal.

53:52.333 --> 53:54.800
[tense percussive tones]

53:54.867 --> 53:56.367
- You're
going to die.

53:56.433 --> 53:57.867
- Not today!

53:59.900 --> 54:00.934
- That hurt!

54:10.500 --> 54:13.300
Tie that motherfuckin'
Nazi up!

54:13.367 --> 54:15.667
- Beecher, come on, baby.

54:15.734 --> 54:16.767
Come on.

54:18.800 --> 54:21.367
- [screaming]

54:24.967 --> 54:28.000
Hey, motherfucker,
do you remember this?

54:29.834 --> 54:30.900
[all screaming]

54:34.100 --> 54:36.133
- He shitted on him!
- Oh, what the fuck?

54:36.200 --> 54:41.033
[laughter]

54:41.100 --> 54:42.633
- Sieg heil, baby!

54:42.700 --> 54:44.800
Sieg-fucking-heil!

54:46.533 --> 54:48.200
- We think we know
what we need.

54:48.266 --> 54:51.200
We spend our time figuring out
how to get what we want,

54:51.266 --> 54:54.066
who can help us,
who's in the way.

54:54.133 --> 54:56.233
We make our moves
and sometimes we get lucky.

54:56.300 --> 54:59.133
We get exactly
what we want...

54:59.200 --> 55:01.133
And life gets worse.

55:01.200 --> 55:03.433
Simple truth number 22:

55:03.500 --> 55:05.767
be careful what you
wish for, brother.

55:05.834 --> 55:07.967
Be very, very careful.

55:10.967 --> 55:14.433
[tense jazzy music]

55:14.500 --> 55:21.533
♪ ♪

56:08.066 --> 56:10.100
[bright tone]
